# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ACAO_0000121> (permanent mold casting production process)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ACAO_0000121> "ISO 3522:2007(en)")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ACAO_0000121> "permanent mold casting production process"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ACAO_0000121> "Casting formed in a metal mould, the molten metal being introduced by gravity and solidification under atmospheric pressure.")
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ACAO_0000121> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ACAO_0000106>)
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ACAO_0000121> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000051> ObjectIntersectionOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ACAO_0000133> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ACAO_0000022> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ACAO_0000014>))))
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ACAO_0000121> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000051> ObjectIntersectionOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ACAO_0000133> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000057> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ACAO_0000137>))))

